              <span>🚀 No Gatekeepers, just vibes</span>
            </div>
            <h2 className="text-5xl sm:text-8xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 max-w-5xl leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">
              Access the GPA Bag <span className="gradient-text italic">Rent Free.</span>
            </h2>
            <p className="text-lg sm:text-2xl text-slate-500 max-w-3xl mb-12 font-medium leading-relaxed">
              Skip the stress. Access all your module resources <span className="text-emerald-600 font-bold">anytime, anywhere, and 100% freely.</span> Fast-track your study sessions and stay winning, <span className="text-emerald-600 font-bold underline decoration-emerald-200 decoration-4 italic">no cap.</span>
            </p>
            <div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 w-full sm:w-auto">
              <button 
